				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Map a key to player 4 Start instead of player 2 Start, and use a controller reading routine that effectively ORs together the bits from controllers 1 and 3 and from controllers 2 and 4. That way, your game logic sees both the mic and player 2 Start.</div>

